 {"id":"bd-1lg.14","title":"E2E test: Galaxy-brain decision card standalone embedding","description":"End-to-end test: Embed galaxy-brain decision card widget in a minimal non-FrankenTUI application (raw crossterm). Verify: (1) Widget renders correctly standalone, (2) Progressive disclosure levels work, (3) No FrankenTUI runtime required, (4) Evidence data can be injected externally. This validates the adoption wedge. LOGGING SPEC: Assert galaxybrain.render span even without full FrankenTUI runtime. Assert widget works in isolation.","status":"open","priority":0,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-02-13T18:01:13.374121668Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-13T18:05:59.220574401Z","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["adoption","e2e","galaxybrain","ring3","test"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-1lg.14","depends_on_id":"bd-1lg","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:25:59Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-1lg.14","depends_on_id":"bd-1lg.8","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:25:59Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
 {"id":"bd-1lg.15","title":"Accessibility: screen reader support and high-contrast mode","description":"Accessibility support: semantic widget roles (button, listbox, treeview, dialog, textfield), ARIA-like attribute propagation to screen readers via terminal accessibility protocols, high-contrast color theme, keyboard-only navigation for all widgets, focus indicator visibility. TRACING: span 'a11y.announce' with fields: widget_role, announcement_text. LOG: DEBUG for accessibility events. METRICS: counter a11y_announcements_total.","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2026-02-13T18:08:26.286719257Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-02-25T02:58:38.432269329Z","closed_at":"2026-02-25T02:58:38.432244452Z","close_reason":"done","source_repo":".","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"labels":["a11y","accessibility","ring3","widgets"],"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-1lg.15","depends_on_id":"bd-1lg","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:25:59Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""},{"issue_id":"bd-1lg.15","depends_on_id":"bd-1lg.1","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-02-24T21:25:59Z","created_by":"import","metadata":"{}","thread_id":""}]}
